OL,3,CMan charged after 87-year-old
OL,4,C'kidnaped and dumped 15 miles away'
OL,6,FA second man has been charged after an
OL,7,F87-year-old pensioner was forced into
OL,8,Fa car, attacked, and thrown out on a
OL,9,Fdark road 15 miles away.
OL,11,FAzizur Rahman, 39, has been charged
OL,12,Fwith kidnap, robbery, intentional
OL,13,Fstrangulation, and threats to a person
OL,14,Fwith a bladed article.
OL,16,FHe was also charged with threat to
OL,17,Fkill, Section 18 assault, and
OL,18,Fperverting the course of justice.
