OL,3,CMan charged after 87-year-old
OL,4,C'kidnaped and dumped 15 miles away'
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police said the
OL,7,Fpensioner had been walking home at 9pm
OL,8,Fon 15 September on Lee Street, Oldham,
OL,9,Fwhen he says he was forced into a
OL,10,Fblack car, before demands were made
OL,11,Ffor his money and personal items.
OL,13,FThe 87-year-old attacked and
OL,14,Feventually pushed out of the car on a
OL,15,Fdark road in the Rishworth area of
OL,16,FWest Yorkshire.
OL,18,FHe managed to find help by knocking on
OL,19,Fa door at around 10:40pm, the force
OL,20,Fadded.
