OL,3,CMan charged after 87-year-old
OL,4,C'kidnaped and dumped 15 miles away'
OL,6,FA second man, Shohad Miah, 24, from
OL,7,FRoyton, was charged with kidnap,
OL,8,Fgrievous bodily harm, robbery and
OL,9,Fintentional strangulation, on Tuesday
OL,10,F24 September.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Emma Hulston, from
OL,13,FGMP's Major Incident Team, said the
OL,14,Fforce "continued to make good
OL,15,Fprogress" following the "shocking
OL,16,Fincident".
