OL,3,CMan charged after 87-year-old
OL,4,C'kidnaped and dumped 15 miles away'
OL,6,F"We understand the concern from local
OL,7,Fresidents and those further afield
OL,8,Facross Greater Manchester after
OL,9,Fhearing of what happened to the
OL,10,Felderly man, we do believe it was an
OL,11,Fisolated incident with no wider threat
OL,12,Fto the public," she added.
OL,14,F"Specialist officers are supporting
OL,15,Fthe victim whilst he recovers from
OL,16,Fthis traumatic ordeal and we have an
OL,17,Finvestigation team working hard behind
OL,18,Fthe scenes to investigate fully and
OL,19,Fbuild a timeline of events leading up
OL,20,Fto this incident."
